DataSelectionDefinition.Description: Datenselektion die das frühere Studium in BRD ausliest. Registerkarte "Früheres/Externes Studium"

HqlDataSelection.Query: select studyBefore.firstStudyInGermanyTerm.year AS jahrBrd, firstStudyInGermanyTerm_termTypeValue.defaulttext AS semBrd, ftU.value AS EnSemBrd from Student AS student left join student.person as person left join person.studyBefore as studyBefore left join studyBefore.firstStudyInGermanyTerm.termTypeValue as firstStudyInGermanyTerm_termTypeValue left join Foreigntext ftU on (ftU.table = 'term_type' AND ftU.column = 'defaulttext' and ftU.language = 5 AND ftU.objectid = firstStudyInGermanyTerm_termTypeValue.id) where person.id = :personId
